they can do more damage to their evil foes.<br>
<br>
SKs would be less tainted by the blows of the undead,<br>
but would lack a holy nights ability to damage them.<br>
There spells should be of great harm to the living,<br>
not the undead.  They cannot master the undead for<br>
they themselves, live, and breed with the power that<br>
has mastered them.<br>
<br>
Warriors are the masters of tank, living or dead.<br>
Spells bounce off them, they do not wiggle their<br>
fingers in combat.  They slash, bash, and grind<br>
there way through the enemy.  They have no<br>
penalty to the foe they fight, nor reap in the<br>
spells they find lying on their victim.<br>
<br>
Paladins should be able to damage undead more with spell/melee combo.<br>
Paladins should damage living with normal melee.<br>
Paladins should take more damage from undead.<br>
Paladins should suffer slight less damage from living.<br>
<br>
SKs should be able to damage living more with spell/melee combo.<br>
SKs should damage undead with normal melee.<br>
SKs should take less damage from undead.<br>
SKs should take more damage from the living.<br>
<br>
Warriors should be able to do better melee damage on living and undead than either SK or Paladin, because we have no use for spells.<br>
Warriors should take little damage from undead.<br>
Warriors should take little damage from living. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/udobbanz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>dobbanz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/cons RED</span><br>  Posts: 305<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/18/02 12:54:15 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1430.topic&index=37>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Tank balanceing from a old outdated paladin. What do u t</span><hr size=1> Because you started this thread with mindess gibbering seventh. Paladins are supposed to be inferior tanks to warriors.  Remember that spell book you have? That is why you are supposed to be a worse tank when compared to warriors. Thats ALL the time btw, not 60%, not 20% ALL the time. You ARE supposed to be decent tanks though. The problem is that Verant overcompensated when they brought you back up in power from when hybrid classes sucked.<br>
